<RefNameDiv>
<RefName><command>satellite-sync</command></RefName>
<RefPurpose>
Incrementally synchronize an RHN Satellite's DB data and RPM repository with Red Hat's RHN DB and RPM repository.
</RefPurpose>
</RefNameDiv>

